dct_title_s: Long Beach Island, Ocean County, New Jersey (Sheet 6)
dct_description_sm: "Aug. 1930." Includes location map, streets and specials index, key, key map and text. "4915." "Including boroughs of: Beach Haven, Ship Bottom-Beach Arlington, Harvey Cedars (High Point) and Surf City and the following resorts, all in Long Beach Township: North Beach Haven, Spray Beach, Beach Haven Bay Vista, Beach Haven Gardens, Beach Haven Terrace, Beach Haven Crest and Brant Beach."
